In re Resignation of Johnson.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Johnson (1991), 61 Ohio St.3d 1203.]

(No. 91-1277 Submitted July 17, 1991 Decided July 24, 1991.)

The resignation of Barbara Lynn Johnson as an attorney, Registration No. 0030533, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
